source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_SEQ_00<tab>The voracious Vath is staring towards the southern sky.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_SEQ_00<tab>Le Vathe vorace est tourné vers le sud, le regard perdu dans le vague...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_SEQ_01<tab>The voracious Vath has asked you to collect four yellow pebbles for him. Such pebbles can be found in the craters to the south of Anyx Trine.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_SEQ_01<tab>Le Vathe vorace vous a demandé de lui rapporter quatre <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8AD40302 /var>. D'après lui, on en trouve au Déclin d'Avalonia.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_SEQ_02<tab>You successfully obtain the requested stones. Take them back to the voracious Vath at Loth ast Vath.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_SEQ_02<tab>Donnez les pierres que vous avez ramassées au Vathe vorace.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_SEQ_03<tab>The voracious Vath is impressed with how quickly you retrieved the yellow pebbles. He tells you that they are one of the main ingredients of Gnathic firesand, but seems uneager to go into the details of what else is required.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_SEQ_03<tab>Visiblement, les pierres que vous avez ramenées sont recouvertes de soufre, que le Vathe vorace souhaite recueillir pour fabriquer de la poudre de bâton à feu.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the pebbles to the voracious Vath.
TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_000<tab>Are you looking for work, hunter? You come at a good time. We have work for you. We would like you to bring us some materials.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_000<tab>Ksss... Généreu<var 08 E905 ((se)) ((x)) /var> chasseu<var 08 E905 ((se)) ((r)) /var>, vous voulez encore m'aider<var 1D /var>? J'ai besoin d'un minerai particulier.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_001<tab>To the south of the place men call Anyx Trine, there are craters. In these craters are yellow pebbles. Please collect four yellow pebbles from these craters. Please collect these pebbles and bring them to me.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_001<tab>Dans cet endroit que les humains appellent Annexe Trine, on trouve <var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E8AD40302 /var> par terre. J'en voudrais quatre, kssss...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_010<tab>The yellow pebbles should be in the craters. The craters are south of Anyx Trine.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_010<tab>Dans cet endroit que les humains appellent Annexe Trine, on trouve <var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E8AD40302 /var> par terre. J'en voudrais quatre, kssss...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_021<tab>Thank you, generous hunter. You waste no time.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_021<tab>Quelle rapidité, ksss... Merci encore de votre générosité, humain<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_022<tab>These stones are used to make Gnathic firesand. We grind the stones and mix them with our...errr... <click> <click> <click> <click> Actually, we would prefer not to go into details.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ301_01793_NANKAEATER_000_022<tab>Ksss... La poudre jaune qui s'est déposée sur cette pierre est du soufre. C'est l'ingrédient principal de la poudre de bâton à feu. Je ne peux pas vous dévoiler les autres, c'est trop gênant à dire... Ksss.
